{"tid":145181,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"IVE EE HD 有嘢唔識 ??? 搵鏗哥啦","createTime":"2017-03-06T05:04:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-23T11:40:30.000Z","uid":14170,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"364218e3982ae6e881b7c4db754fb8eaebfc29e2","tid":145181,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T05:04:37.000Z","msg":"話時話 Sem 2 已經過左一半 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果你有野唔識，或者上堂跟唔到既話，我建議你把握時間盡快解決佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n歡迎搵鏗哥幫你搞搞佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我係 HKIVE 電機工程高級文憑 2014 年畢業生，依家係 HKU 電機工程三年級學生，畢左業呢幾年都有幫讀緊 HD 既同學仔補習，如果你有興趣想搵個私補老師可以 Telegram PM 我 ( id: hanggggor )。<br />\n<br />\n我可以教既 Sem2 科目：<br />\nInstrumentation &amp; Measurement<br />\nElectrical Engineering Principles<br />\nDigital Electronics<br />\nEngineering Math 2<br />\n<br />\n呢張係我 HD 既成績表：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c200xVf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc200xVf.png&h=71ab67e4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"da4948e3f3dde2d7e5aadb05df7b45eb22fc318a","tid":145181,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T05:05:30.000Z","msg":"UP 錯圖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2d1JN5F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2d1JN5F.jpg&h=6100c6ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2a67b6f7e026992470bf09d28071b0d08b900bdf","tid":145181,"uid":53278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T05:06:03.000Z","msg":"你貼張乜撚野出黎呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1338634a6887ae7420e599c8114e4052a68e5ef","tid":145181,"uid":39381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T05:07:58.000Z","msg":"樓主send左cv未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=